channel.title: My Client.java Disappeared!
channel.description: So, I was editing it as I got an error on my Compiler. I did CTRL+S and then I closed it, I got an error again and so i tried to go into Client.java again but it wasn't there. It isn't in my recycle bin... I don't know where it went, I have a backup but I had loads of extra things there.
